      <odd id="aspace_67ff854c8b0130ed6b7106e07051e83f">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 26-C (YRG 26-C), Records of officers and faculty of the Yale Law School. The original minutes for 1950-1981 on reels 3 and 4 are held by the Yale Law School.</p>  
      </odd>
